CREATE TABLE demographic_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  city VARCHAR(255),
  state VARCHAR(255),
  population INT,
  median_income DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

  population INT,
  ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
  age_group VARCHAR(20)
);
